      Parameters:
      replenishmentId - for ID of the replenishment
      medicationId - for ID of the Medication to be replenished
      medicationName - for name of the Medication to be replenished
      amount - for the stock amount to be replenished
      id - type AdministratorID for the admin who endorsed
      endorsedby - for Staff
      dateOfRequest - date of the request of the replenishment
